Responsibilities

  Examine procurement data from GeBIZ to ensure consistency.
  Analyse procurement data, identify trend, develop insights and present key findings.
  Develop reports, dashboards and visualisations.

Qualification

  Qualifications with a major in data management and analysis or business or IT or Engineering. A minor in general procurement function such as purchasing, sourcing, operations management, supply chain or logistics is preferred.
  Proficient in data sorting and analysis tools such as Access, Excel or BI.
  Strong quantitative and analytical skill and statistics knowledge.
  Good written and presentation skills


The successful candidate will be appointed on a 1 year traineeship agreement.

We regret to inform only successful candidates will be notified.